    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/586d197d62d00c8f2fdfb95d9fc88aea.avif?t=1768933053\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>踏入「九舆」：一场融合传统仙侠与潮流幻想结合的江湖冒险！</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏B站账号：归风记</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏抖音账号：<strong>归风记_墨镜猫工作室</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏官方QQ群（禁言）：1063918577</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>关于我们</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">我们是一支来自广州的5人团队，该项目的性质是<u><strong>单机买断制独立游戏</strong></u>噢——☆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>我们的游戏正在寻找发行商中…合作请联系wx：ookamimomo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/a1e4dbe3148ddbfc21115982147035fd.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>《归风记》是一款都市玄幻仙侠主题的回合制JRPG游戏</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">名为【九舆】的奇幻大陆，三界大战千百年后，来到了现代，这个人与妖共同和谐生活的世界，仙和魔已经成了过去的传说，这个聚焦在名为流风城的都市的故事就此展开。你将扮演一个来自玄武山白凌派的人类少女侠客，和可以化为神器“凌玦剑”的神秘灵兽咕啾，在这个城市遇到形形色色的伙伴，寻找五行魂石，化身形态各异的灵兽，最终一同踏上打败魔族，拯救流风城的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/6012fb15dff232fa6b72423634980850.avif?t=1768933053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras_big/6012fb15dff232fa6b72423634980850.webp?t=1768933053 width=1560 height=533 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/5aba27b8ca350c078e86b11807d700aa.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=319 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/ef66e0c7d2c22411c0486c535991bb70.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=437 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/32f21ffeaa0523e58a1a36fdfd17a1dd.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=163 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·探索奇幻的「九舆」世界观，体验融合了五行生克、山海经异兽、中国传统神话的原创故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·与数十位风格迥异、个性鲜明的伙伴相遇，深入了解他们各自的背景故事与羁绊，通过主线与丰富的个人支线任务招募他们并肩作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·在架空的仙侠背景下，融入独特的设定与潮流幻想都市风貌，打造耳目一新的视觉与叙事体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/a9cbf32eb90cc0cc3221d3bbf1e75b10.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/86a1063432a26ca6278028e6aa6cba0c.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=163 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/f1448a6f9a619e35613c624ebb96408a.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=417 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">·在细节满满的2D卡通横版世界中自由探索精心设计的箱庭式地图，各具鲜明文化与视觉风格的流风城五大特色区域等着你来踏上旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·地图设计注重玩家体验：目标清晰可见、传送便捷、彩蛋丰富，让玩家在体验核心玩法的过程里充分沉浸其中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/5ff96171461b0cf73432dea75c17e1c3.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/2682fd884191d27cc1b7660e0ec5b377.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/021785e8e3baceb46fbd4adc7ef558cb.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·特色化形变身玩法，无论是主角还是伙伴，都可以在探索过程中可以变身各式各样的奇妙灵兽——灵活运用灵兽形态技能进行场景解谜，开启隐藏区域与宝藏，让探索充满趣味与发现感吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/ebc3003caaa2c096be7cab8689a2c657.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=880 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/e8093f88bbe848d6d7d7d93ed4dee350.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=163 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·主打PVE回合制战斗，基于五行属性相克核心机制的回合制2V2战斗，通过精心搭配你的小队成员与技能组合，制定克敌制胜的策略吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·每个角色拥有丰富的技能池，配合多种可收集与额外学习的武功秘籍，组建独属于你的、丰富多变的战斗策略吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·获取资源强化你的伙伴与队伍，体验紧张刺激的BOSS战、挑战各式各样的武馆，突破武学境界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/34056cfa91bc19277f213a476e148452.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/ac90d86bb5d0185b6d25584ecd0b1d2b.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/afd46f006fb8b26c2cd87f0364d2ea05.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=163 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">·感受 “酸性潮流色”碰撞“新国风”的独特美术风格！ 采用高饱和度、高对比度的鲜明色彩与波普漫画、涂鸦艺术结合的萌系二次元风格，带来强烈的视觉冲击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/c93a048da5800e6871a53a961ae21066.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/6012fb15dff232fa6b72423634980850.avif?t=1768933053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras_big/6012fb15dff232fa6b72423634980850.webp?t=1768933053 width=1560 height=533 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/f25ea73436c87dcf575c86bfc7a6097e.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=331 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/5af6c9c553b541616263db94c8e0545d.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=1000 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/df679a42fb8126b47ca6b9b8ae0eb7a5.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=939 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/b586353a370213f01ed304d268131195.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=1060 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/e05d36defefecdce90e141af459b46db.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=1053 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/cdcb263d74585cbb97e611845389390f.avif?t=1768933053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras_big/cdcb263d74585cbb97e611845389390f.avif?t=1768933053 width=1560 height=728 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>踏上归风之旅，在传统与潮流的交汇点，书写九舆的仙侠新篇章！</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316900/extras/b6430c647d9f3cce17034d6c787837ea.avif?t=1768933053\" width=1560 height=791 /></span></p>",
